=== Using the template ===
Type '''<code><nowiki>{{</nowiki>Emoticon|''code''|''size''<nowiki>}}</nowiki></code>''' for insert a emoticon.

==Examples==
{|
!Type
!Result
|-
|<pre>{{Emoticon|O:)}}</pre>
|{{en/Emoticon|O:)}}
|-
|<pre>{{Emoticon|;)}}</pre>
|{{en/Emoticon|;)}}
|-
|<pre>{{Emoticon|:O}}</pre>
|{{en/Emoticon|:O}}
|-
|<pre>{{Emoticon|Smiley|L}}</pre>
|{{en/Emoticon|Smiley|L}}
|-
|<pre>{{Emoticon|Confused|S}}</pre>
|{{en/Emoticon|Confused|S}}
|-
|<pre>{{Emoticon|Cool|M}}</pre>
|{{en/Emoticon|Cool|M}}
|}

==Available sizes==
*Size '''L''' = 120px
*Size '''M''' = 48px
*Size '''S''' = 22px
*Size other (or nothing) =22px

